OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Around two million more British        
OL,6, citizens living overseas will be able  
OL,7, to register for a vote in general      
OL,8, elections following a rule change.     
OL,10,FPreviously, people who left the UK more
OL,11,Fthan 15 years ago lost their right to  
OL,12,Fvote.                                  
OL,14,FHowever, this rule has now been        
OL,15,Fabolished under the Election Act 2022. 
OL,17,FAffected British citizens will now be  
OL,18,Fable to register in the last           
OL,19,Fconstituency they were signed up in    
OL,20,Fbefore leaving the UK.                 
